  "text": "Diseases. Extracting protein-protein interactions involves searching for two proteins in the text and determining whether they interact with each other. Similarly, extracting the relationship between gene functions and diseases also involves searching for gene names and disease names simultaneously in the literature and then determining whether a particular gene is related to a certain disease [CITATION_1] .",
